<br>
Here's what my experience has been so far, up to level 5 (100% solo):<br>
<br>
Buff yourself with your free spells--the ones you didn't have to buy, scribe or &quot;mem&quot;. Spells are given to you instantly, and &quot;mem&quot;-ing them takes all of 1 second--as fast as you can drag it to your skill bar. Oh, and buffs don't wear out--unless you zone into a major city or die.<br>
<br>
Find a blue or yellow mob (even con or better), beat it to death.<br>
<br>
Heal yourself completely, have 50% mana left.<br>
<br>
By the time you find another mob to fight (about 30 seconds or so), your mana is back to 100%.<br>
<br>
Rinse, repeat.<br>
<br>
I just became a Friar--and got yet more skills and spells that I haven't tried yet. <p><html><body>
